<topic id="reusables-working-with-databases">
  <title>Reusable Components in Working with Databases</title>
  <body>
    <!--Create a DataSource initial steps-->
    <p><ph id="open-ds"><ph conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/Open-the-preferences-page"/> and
        go to <uicontrol>Data Sources</uicontrol>.</ph></p>
    <p><ph id="click-new">Click the <uicontrol><image href="../../img/Add16.png"/>New</uicontrol>
        button in the <uicontrol>Data Sources</uicontrol> panel.</ph></p>
    <p><ph id="unique-name">Enter a unique name for the data source.</ph></p>
    <p><ph id="step6">Click the <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol> button to finish the data source
        configuration.</ph></p>
    <p><ph id="select-driver-class">Select the most appropriate <uicontrol>Driver
        class</uicontrol>.</ph></p>
    <p><ph id="click-new-connection">Click the <uicontrol><image href="../../img/Add16.png"
          />New</uicontrol> button in the <uicontrol>Connections</uicontrol> panel.</ph></p>
    <p><ph id="unique-name-connection">Enter a unique name for the connection.</ph></p>
    <p><ph id="click-ok-connection">Click the <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol> button to finish the
        connection configuration.</ph></p>
    <!--Contextual Menu Actions-->
    <section id="contextual_menu_actions">
      <title>General Contextual Menu Actions</title>
      <p>For relational databases, the following general actions are available in the contextual
        menu of the <xref
          href="../../topics/relational-database-explorer.dita#relational-database-explorer"
            ><uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref>, depending on the node in which
        it is invoked:</p>
      <p>
        <dl>
          <dlentry id="refresh">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/Refresh16.png" id="image_qnr_4fw_sr"
                />Refresh</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Performs a refresh on the selected node.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol>Disconnect</uicontrol> (available on <uicontrol><image
                  href="../../img/DbConnection16.gif"/>Connection</uicontrol> nodes)</dt>
            <dd>Closes the current database connection. If a table is already open, you are warned
              to close it before proceeding.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/Options16.png"/>Configure Database
                Sources</uicontrol> (available on <uicontrol><image
                  href="../../img/DbConnection16.gif"/>Connection</uicontrol> nodes)</dt>
            <dd>Opens the <xref
                href="../../topics/preferences-data-sources.dita#preferences-data-sources"
                  ><uicontrol>Data Sources</uicontrol> preferences page</xref> where you can
              configure both data sources and connections.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="edit-table">
            <dt><uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol> (available on <uicontrol><image
                  href="../../img/DbTable16.gif" id="image_uf2_njz_tr"/>Table</uicontrol>
              nodes)</dt>
            <dd>Opens the selected table in the <xref
                href="../../topics/relational-table-explorer.dita#relational-table-explorer"
                  ><uicontrol>Table Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref>.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="export-to-xml">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/Export2Xml16.gif" id="image_i1w_1vz_tr"/>Export to
                XML</uicontrol> (available on <uicontrol><image href="../../img/DbTable16.gif"
                />Table</uicontrol> nodes)</dt>
            <dd>Opens the <uicontrol>Export Criteria</uicontrol> dialog box <ph
                product="editor editorEclipse developer developerEclipse">(a thorough description of
                this dialog box can be found in the <xref
                  href="../../tasks/import-db-table-content-to-xml.dita">Import from Database</xref>
                chapter)</ph>.</dd>
          </dlentry>
        </dl>
      </p>
    </section>
    <p>
      <dl>
        <dlentry id="compare">
          <dt><uicontrol>Compare</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Compares two selected resources<ph product="author developer editor"> using the <xref
                href="../../topics/file-comparison.dita#file-comparison"><uicontrol>Compare
                  Files</uicontrol> tool</xref></ph>.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="unregister">
          <dt><uicontrol>Unregister</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Removes the selected schema from the XML Schema Repository.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="view-schema">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/OpenSchema16.png" id="image_nmy_35z_tr"
              />View</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the selected schema in <ph keyref="product"/>.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="register">
          <dt><uicontrol>Register </uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens a dialog box for adding a new schema file in the DB XML repository. In this
            dialog box, you enter a collection name and the necessary schema files. Schema
            dependencies management can be done by using the <uicontrol>Add</uicontrol> and
              <uicontrol>Remove</uicontrol> buttons.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="add-container">
          <dt><uicontrol>Add container</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Adds a new child container to the current one.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="add-resource">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/AddFile16.gif" id="image_e5r_12w_sr"/>Add
              resource</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Adds a new resource to the folder.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="open">
          <dt><uicontrol>Open</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the selected resource in the editor.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="save-as">
          <dt><uicontrol>Save As</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to save the selected resource as a file on disk.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="rename">
          <dt><uicontrol>Rename</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Renames the current resource</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="move">
          <dt><uicontrol>Move</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Moves the current resource to a new container (also available through drag and
            drop).</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="delete">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/Remove16.png"/>Delete</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Deletes the current container.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="copy-location">
          <dt><uicontrol>Copy location</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to copy (to the clipboard) an application-specific URL for the resource
            that can then be used for various actions, such as opening or transforming the
            resources.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="properties">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/DockableFrameProperties16.png"
              />Properties</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Shows various properties of the current container.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="configure_data_sources">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/Options16.png"/>Configure Database
              Sources</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref
              href="../../topics/preferences-data-sources.dita#preferences-data-sources"
                ><uicontrol>Data Sources</uicontrol> preferences page</xref> where you can configure
            both data sources and connections.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="disconnect">
          <dt><uicontrol>Disconnect</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Stops the connection.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="new_file">
          <dt><uicontrol>New File</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Creates a new file on the connection, in the current folder.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="new_folder">
          <dt><uicontrol>New Folder</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Creates a new folder on the connection.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="import_folders">
          <dt><uicontrol>Import Folders</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Imports folders on the server.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="import_files">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/AddFile16.gif" id="image_oky_zdw_sr"/>Import
              Files</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to add a new file on the connection, in the current folder.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="export">
          <dt><uicontrol>Export</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to export the folder on the remote connection to a local folder.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="cut_webdav">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/Cut16.png" id="image_phd_4z1_5r"
            />Cut</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Removes the current selection and places it in the clipboard.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="copy_webdav">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/Copy16.png" id="image_q1c_2st_tr"
            />Copy</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Copies the current selection into the clipboard.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="paste">
          <dt><uicontrol>
              <image href="../../img/Paste16.png" id="image_ks3_4qt_tr"/>Paste</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Pastes the copied selection.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="find_replace_in_files" product="author developer editor">
          <dt><uicontrol>
              <image href="../../img/SearchInPath16.png" id="image_j32_fpf_wr"/>Find/Replace in
              Files</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref
              href="../../topics/find-and-replace-text-in-files.dita#find-and-replace-text-in-files"
                ><uicontrol>Find/Replace in Files</uicontrol> dialog box</xref> that allows you to
            find and replace text in multiple files from the connection.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="add-library">
          <dt><uicontrol>Add Library</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to add a new library.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="insert-xml-instance">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/AddFile16.gif"/>Insert XML Instance</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to add a new XML resource directly into the database root. See <xref
              href="../../topics/xhive-parser-configuration.dita"><ph keyref="xhiveDB"/> Parser
              Configuration</xref> for more details.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="insert-non-xml-instance">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../../img/AddNonXmlResource16.gif"/>Insert non-XML
              Instance</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to add a new non-XML resource directly in the database root.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
  </body>
</topic>
